comments.body:
That patch also adds a URL-encoded parameter, oneShot, that when true, will close the consumer on completion of the request.  Like this:

{noformat}
curl --no-keepalive -o message \
	"http://localhost:8161/api/message/TEST?type=queue&clientId=GETID1&readTimeout=1000&oneShot=true"
{noformat}
